hopobject.body: Do you know the number for ? herbal pharmacy battlefield blvd Other vishing schemes involve the use of automated systems to call specific area codes and play a message about a local or regional bank in the area. Scammers can record the real bank's phone greeting to make you think it's a legitimate call from your bank and lure you into providing your account number or other information. They might also use caller ID spoofing technology to display a false name or number on your phone.
